snippet.title: Brawlout - Paco Character Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
PACO, the luchador grappler joins the cast of fighters in Brawlout!

Brawlout is the upcoming platform fighter, coming early 2017 to PlayStation 4, Xbox One and PC.

Sign up for the closed beta at www.brawlout.com
